            <title>[Graph database] 使用docker安裝memgraph &amp; python簡易連線</title>
            <link>http://localhost:1313/2024/03/24/graph-database-%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8docker%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%9Dmemgraph/</link>
            <pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 06:42:36 +0000</pubDate>
            <guid>http://localhost:1313/2024/03/24/graph-database-%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8docker%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%9Dmemgraph/</guid>
            <description>&lt;ul class=&#34;wp-block-list&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;li&gt;&#xA;    使用docker desktop&#xA;  &lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;``&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;什麼是-graph-database-&#34;&gt;什麼是 Graph database ？&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%9B%BE%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;    &gt;Graph database簡稱GDB&lt;/a&gt;,是一個使用圖結構進行語意查詢的資料庫，它使用節點、邊和屬性來表示和儲存資料。 該系統的關鍵概念是圖，它直接將儲存中的資料項，與資料節點和節點間表示關係的邊的集合相關聯&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;目前有哪些GraphDB,排名:&lt;a href=&#34;https://db-engines.com/en/ranking/graph+dbmsmemgraph&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noreferrer noopener&#34;&gt;圖形資料庫排名&lt;/a&gt;以及所有&lt;a href=&#34;https://db-engines.com/en/ranking&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noreferrer noopener&#34;&gt;受歡迎程度對資料庫管理系統進行排名&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;docker-desktop-安裝-memgraph&#34;&gt;docker desktop 安裝 memgraph &lt;figure class=&#34;wp-block-image size-large&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; width=&#34;1024&#34; height=&#34;579&#34; src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/uploads/2024/03/image-1-1024x579.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; class=&#34;wp-image-1030&#34; srcset=&#34;http://localhost:1313/uploads/2024/03/image-1-1024x579.png 1024w, http://localhost:1313/uploads/2024/03/image-1-300x170.png 300w, http://localhost:1313/uploads/2024/03/image-1-768x434.png 768w, http://localhost:1313/uploads/2024/03/image-1.png 1266w&#34; sizes=&#34;auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px&#34; /&gt; &lt;/figure&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;以在 localhost:7687 看到 memgraph 的介面了。&lt;figure class=&#34;wp-block-image size-large&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; width=&#34;1024&#34; height=&#34;551&#34; src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/uploads/2024/03/image-2-1024x551.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; class=&#34;wp-image-1031&#34; srcset=&#34;http://localhost:1313/uploads/2024/03/image-2-1024x551.png 1024w, http://localhost:1313/uploads/2024/03/image-2-300x161.png 300w, http://localhost:1313/uploads/2024/03/image-2-768x413.png 768w, http://localhost:1313/uploads/2024/03/image-2-1536x827.png 1536w, http://localhost:1313/uploads/2024/03/image-2-2048x1102.png 2048w&#34; sizes=&#34;auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px&#34; /&gt; &lt;/figure&gt; &lt;figure class=&#34;wp-block-image size-large&#34;&gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; width=&#34;1024&#34; height=&#34;638&#34; src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/uploads/2024/03/image-3-1024x638.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; class=&#34;wp-image-1032&#34; srcset=&#34;http://localhost:1313/uploads/2024/03/image-3-1024x638.png 1024w, http://localhost:1313/uploads/2024/03/image-3-300x187.png 300w, http://localhost:1313/uploads/2024/03/image-3-768x478.png 768w, http://localhost:1313/uploads/2024/03/image-3-1536x956.png 1536w, http://localhost:1313/uploads/2024/03/image-3-2048x1275.png 2048w&#34; sizes=&#34;auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px&#34; /&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;點擊左方的Datasets 找 CORA: Scientific publications classified into seven categories&lt;figure class=&#34;wp-block-image size-large&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; width=&#34;1024&#34; height=&#34;550&#34; src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/uploads/2024/03/image-4-1024x550.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; class=&#34;wp-image-1033&#34; srcset=&#34;http://localhost:1313/uploads/2024/03/image-4-1024x550.png 1024w, http://localhost:1313/uploads/2024/03/image-4-300x161.png 300w, http://localhost:1313/uploads/2024/03/image-4-768x413.png 768w, http://localhost:1313/uploads/2024/03/image-4-1536x826.png 1536w, http://localhost:1313/uploads/2024/03/image-4.png 1920w&#34; sizes=&#34;auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px&#34; /&gt; &lt;/figure&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;執行完成後點擊 run query&lt;figure class=&#34;wp-block-image size-large&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; width=&#34;1024&#34; height=&#34;550&#34; src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/uploads/2024/03/image-5-1024x550.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; class=&#34;wp-image-1034&#34; srcset=&#34;http://localhost:1313/uploads/2024/03/image-5-1024x550.png 1024w, http://localhost:1313/uploads/2024/03/image-5-300x161.png 300w, http://localhost:1313/uploads/2024/03/image-5-768x413.png 768w, http://localhost:1313/uploads/2024/03/image-5-1536x826.png 1536w, http://localhost:1313/uploads/2024/03/image-5.png 1920w&#34; sizes=&#34;auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px&#34; /&gt; &lt;/figure&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;會出現下方成功的結果&lt;figure class=&#34;wp-block-image size-large&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; width=&#34;1024&#34; height=&#34;591&#34; src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/uploads/2024/03/image-1024x591.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; class=&#34;wp-image-1027&#34; srcset=&#34;http://localhost:1313/uploads/2024/03/image-1024x591.png 1024w, http://localhost:1313/uploads/2024/03/image-300x173.png 300w, http://localhost:1313/uploads/2024/03/image-768x443.png 768w, http://localhost:1313/uploads/2024/03/image.png 1355w&#34; sizes=&#34;auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px&#34; /&gt; &lt;/figure&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;python連線&#34;&gt;Python連線&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul class=&#34;wp-block-list&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;li&gt;&#xA;    使用pycharm&#xA;  &lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;官網教學:&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://pypi.org/project/pymgclient/0.1.0/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;    &gt;網址&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;當memgraph建立成功後使用下方程式碼來建立Person&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;pre class=&#34;wp-block-code&#34;&gt;&lt;code lang=&#34;python&#34; class=&#34;language-python line-numbers&#34;&gt;import mgclient&#xA;&#xA;conn = mgclient.connect(host=&#39;127.0.0.1&#39;, port=7687)&#xA;cursor = conn.cursor()&#xA;cursor.execute(&#34;&#34;&#34;&#xA;        CREATE (n:Person {name: &#39;John&#39;})-[e:KNOWS]-&amp;gt;&#xA;               (m:Person {name: &#39;Steve&#39;})&#xA;        RETURN n, e, m&#xA;    &#34;&#34;&#34;)&#xA;&#xA;row = cursor.fetchone()&#xA;print(row[0])  # (:Person {&#39;name&#39;: &#39;John&#39;})&#xA;print(row[1])  # [:KNOWS]&#xA;print(row[2])  # (:Person {&#39;name&#39;: &#39;Steve&#39;})&#xA;&#xA;conn.commit()  # 提交數據(沒有commit就不會真正存進資料庫內)&#xA;# 關閉游標和連線&#xA;cursor.close()&#xA;conn.close()&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;接著在memgraph下sql指令即可看到剛才創建的2筆資料&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;pre class=&#34;wp-block-code&#34;&gt;&lt;code lang=&#34;sql&#34; class=&#34;language-sql&#34;&gt;MATCH (c:Person) RETURN c;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&#xA;</description>
        </item></channel>
